Changelog:

2007-07-15 Revision 1.3

   * Added the option to format NaN and Infinity as desired.

2007-06-19 Revision 1.2

   * Fixed zero-padding.  -1 with #,#.00 was -01.00 and should be -1.00.

2006-07-08 Revision 1.1
